I’ve been spending more time on my YouTube Channel Ysanrocheofficial - Check out the Shorts and Videos. The picture is a Snapshot of one of the latest Video Shorts I made. I’m having fun 😋😁#whitebodysuit#whitefashion#fashionistastyle#ysanroche#ladyinwhite

One of my favourite Spots in Phuket is the Sunset Restaurant where you can watch the Sun go down and Ocean while eating.
I actually planned to fly to Belize in March and wasn’t allowed to transit over New York due to my V status. So I ended up in Phuket where I spent a few months and now returned for a few weeks because I loved it so much.
Definitely one of my most memorable trips for the past 3 years… but I know there can be more 😂😂- there always more on this world to explore❤️❤️😘
Sitting by the beach is like listening to a poem - it captures your heart and enlightens your soul ❤️#lifeislikeapoem #sittingbetgebeach#phukettravel#lifestylephuket#creatingyourdreamlife
Some days are just perfect because you were looking to make them so ❤️❤️😂#thisworldisnotwhatyouthinkitis #worldisheaven #beautifulearth#missonistyle #blondestyle

Such a lovely day at the coolest Beach in Phuket. There a Ridersurf Festival today where you can watch or simply dance to the club sound - probably the best day in Phuket before I’m leaving.
#raiderssurf #phuketkatabeach #katabeachphuket #katabeach #surffestival#surfervibes#bestbeachesintheworld #coolbeaches #partybeach

Just landed yesterday and slept for 12 hours after a stressful trip. I’m just exploring this amazing city and all its beautiful magic #villaggiomall#sweetqatar#ysanroche#qatarshoppong#ladiestravelgram #traveltheworldtoday

This was one of the best days, although there was this hour when pretty much everything seemed to go wrong, from my phone dying while I couldn’t find my driver, then the strap of my dress suddenly broke which could have gotten me in seriously embarrassing situations (in Qatar as a lady)…. But then finally everything turned out well. So I feel loved and protected by this world ❤️❤️❤️life is good if you make it so 😻😘big kisses to you all #dohathepearl#loveyourlife#ysanroche#crazydays#crazyadventures#whenallelsefails

My second favourite place for shopping are the Galleries Lafayettes in Doha. It’s even better than the one in Paris or Berlin. I forgot if there is one in London, but nothing can compare to this one. This lovely Ritz Style Cafe had some lovely teddy bears placed on most tables, 😂they were seriously cute and funny. I made a video with them on my YouTube Channel Ysanrocheofficial. Can’t help it, I’m still a 5-year old deep in my heart sometimes. And I love my childlike nature 😂❤️❤️#arabicnights#dohagallerieslafayettes#blondeladiesrock #qatartravel

I am digging Arabic Music right now. I’m so in love with Doha, I could actually live here and be happy. It is such a difference to deal with “Spiritually Clean” people if some of you know what I mean. People are friendly and open, their eyes shine brighter…. Allah - I’m sorry, but I like it here, I hope you are not mad that Western Society had messed me up 😂😂😂… I will be here more often than you might assume 😂❤️❤️❤️#princessstylefashion #princessstyle #ilovedoha#arabicstyle❤️ #zimmermannfashion #zimmermanndress
